Package: somalign
Title: Align Query SOMs to Fixed Kohonen Reference SOMs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mikhael", "Manurung", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "mikhael.manurung@gmail.com")
Description: Aligns query self-organising maps to fixed 'kohonen' reference maps
    using codebook-level unbalanced entropic optimal transport. Direct
    reference projection is kept as the conservative primary result, with
    auxiliary transport-corrected projection columns for annotation and
    visualisation.
URL: https://mdmanurung.github.io/somalign, https://github.com/mdmanurung/somalign
BugReports: https://github.com/mdmanurung/somalign/issues
